        Returns:

      • suspend

        void suspend()
        Resolution is suspended. If #draw(GLMapView) is invoked, any data that has already been loaded should be rendered, however, no new data should be loaded. The rest of the data may continue loading if resume() is invoked.

        This method does nothing if the current state is not GLResolvable.State.RESOLVING.

      • resume

        void resume()
        Resolution is resumed. This method may be invoked following a call to suspend() to resume loading data.

        This method does nothing if the current state is not GLResolvable.State.SUSPENDED.
